    "This iterative update process aims to enhance the network's predictive capabilities.",
    "The present study employed the Adam optimizer and utilized categorical cross-entropy as the loss function during the model's training.",
    "The experimental configuration involved setting the batch size to 64 and the number of epochs to 90.",
